data.description: Love Where You Live! Exceptional value in fantastic Loveland location! This incredible 4 bed/3 bath home sits on a huge 0.23 acre corner lot featuring an open floor plan, laminate/vinyl flooring throughout, vaulted ceilings, natural lighting, & more. Updated kitchen has stainless steel appliances, gas range, & plenty of cabinet space. Primary bedroom has been converted into a spacious retreat w/ huge closet area & beautiful private 3/4 bath. Large living room, 2nd bedroom, & updated full bathroom complete the amazing main level. Enjoy a finished basement with two additional bedrooms, full bath, rec area, laundry, workshop & storage. Newer furnace, A/C, water heater, & roof- plus radon mitigation can give you peace of mind that the big out of pocket expenses have already been taken care of. Step outside to your large backyard w/ plenty of room to run, play, & garden. Have a boat or need to park a trailer? Gate access from the road allows you to park your toys & keep them hidden. Convenient location close to shopping, dining, Lake Loveland, Boyd Lake, bike trails, & 287. This one is PRICED TO SELL & a MUST SEE!
